---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Section } from '@/components/ui';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Roots On Rise"
  description="Privacy policy for Roots On Rise. Learn how we handle your information when you visit our website."
  showAnnouncement={false}
  noindex={true}
>
  <Section background="tertiary" container="md">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h1 class="font-title font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-dark mb-6">
        <span class="text-primary">privacy</span> policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-dark/70 text-lg">
        Last updated: February 7, 2026
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section container="md">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-dark/80 [&_h2]:font-title [&_h2]:font-bold [&_h2]:text-dark [&_h2]:text-2xl [&_h2]:mt-10 [&_h2]:mb-4 [&_h3]:font-title [&_h3]:font-bold [&_h3]:text-dark [&_h3]:text-xl [&_h3]:mt-8 [&_h3]:mb-3 [&_a]:text-primary [&_a]:underline [&_ul]:list-disc [&_ul]:pl-6 [&_ul]:space-y-2">

      <p>
        Roots On Rise ("we," "us," or "our") operates the website
        <a href="https://rootsonrise.com">rootsonrise.com</a> (the "Site").
        This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information
        when you visit our Site.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

      <h3>Information You Provide</h3>
      <p>
        We may collect information you voluntarily provide, such as your email address
        when you subscribe to our newsletter or contact us at
        <a href="mailto:support@rootsonrise.com">support@rootsonrise.com</a>.
      </p>

      <h3>Automatically Collected Information</h3>
      <p>
        When you visit the Site, certain information may be collected automatically, including:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Browser type and version</li>
        <li>Operating system</li>
        <li>Pages visited and time spent on pages</li>
        <li>Referring website addresses</li>
        <li>IP address (anonymized where possible)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        This information is collected through our hosting provider, Cloudflare, to help us
        understand how visitors use the Site and to maintain its security and performance.
      </p>

      <h2>Amazon Associates Program</h2>
      <p>
        Roots On Rise is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program,
        an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn
        advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com.
      </p>
      <p>
        When you click a link to Amazon on our Site, Amazon may place cookies on your
        device to track purchases. These cookies are governed by
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/help/customer/display.html?nodeId=468496" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Amazon's Privacy Notice</a>.
        We do not control Amazon's data collection practices.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p>
        Our Site uses minimal cookies. We do not use advertising trackers or retargeting pixels.
        The cookies that may be present include:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Security and performance cookies from our hosting provider</li>
        <li><strong>Amazon Associates:</strong> Affiliate tracking cookies when you click links to Amazon</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies will not
        affect your ability to browse the Site.
      </p>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use collected information to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Operate and maintain the Site</li>
        <li>Respond to your inquiries</li>
        <li>Send newsletter updates (only if you have subscribed)</li>
        <li>Understand how visitors use the Site to improve our content</li>
        <li>Protect against security threats</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>
        We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties.
        We may share information with:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Our hosting and CDN provider, for site delivery and security</li>
        <li><strong>Amazon:</strong> When you click affiliate links, Amazon receives referral data</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        While our products are designed for children, our Site is intended for use by
        parents, guardians, and educators. We do not knowingly collect personal information
        from children under 13. If you believe we have inadvertently collected such information,
        please contact us immediately.
      </p>

      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        The Site is a static website hosted on Cloudflare Pages. We do not store user
        accounts, passwords, or payment information. All purchases are completed directly
        through Amazon.com, which has its own security measures.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Request access to any personal information we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your personal information</li>
        <li>Unsubscribe from our newsletter at any time</li>
        <li>Opt out of cookies through your browser settings</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        California residents may have additional rights under the CCPA. EU residents may
        have additional rights under the GDPR. Contact us to exercise any of these rights.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>
        The Site contains links to Amazon.com and social media platforms. These third-party
        sites have their own privacy policies. We are not responsible for their privacy
        practices and encourage you to review their policies.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on
        this page with an updated "Last updated" date.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@rootsonrise.com">support@rootsonrise.com</a><br />
        <strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://rootsonrise.com">rootsonrise.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Layout>
